Here's the custom extension method to be added to the ExcelReader class:

```csharp
public static class MyExtensions
{
    public static string StringConcatenate(this IEnumerable<XElement> elements)
    {
        return string.Concat(elements.Select(e => e.Value));
    }
}
```

